data.description: Cozy 3 bedroom 1 bath one-story home. Granite countertops in the kitchen are a desirable feature due to their durability and aesthetic appeal. A fireplace in the living room adds a warm and inviting atmosphere, especially during colder seasons. bedrooms are good size. Having a fenced yard can be beneficial for privacy and for families with pets or young children. The size of .21 acres is large enough to provide outdoor space without being too overwhelming in terms of maintenance.
